Description: FFmpeg interface for Octave
DescDetail: <<
Implements addframe, avifile, aviinfo, and aviread, using ffmpeg. (and
approximately conforms to the Matlab interface)

This package provides the following functions:
	addframe
	avifile
	aviinfo
	aviread
<<

